entries.journal_entry_description: Speak with Sordaan Xris at the main Rodian hunting camp.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Let Sordaan know that you've successfully defeated Silkthrower the webweaver, Brightclaw the mouf, Paleclaw the mouf, Stoneleg the walluga, Greyclimber the Kashyyyk bantha, and Spiketop the uller.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Tell Sordaan about your Hunting Success
